des:
Listen to a short snippet of inspirational audio as part of your morning Flash Briefing.

To hear more than one clip - check out the main Inspire Me skill in the Alexa App - or visit www.wisewords.fm/inspire-me to find out more.

Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
